  "text": "Mice were administered T863 (5 mg kg Lipidomics The protocol for lipid extraction was adapted from Matyash et al. [CITATION_1] . Frozen cell pellets (5x10 5 cells) were resuspended in ice cold PBS and transferred to glass tubes before the addition of methanol and methyl tert-butyl ether. The tubes were then shaken for 1 h at 4ºC. Water was added to separate the phases before centrifugation at 1,000 x g for 10 min.",
